data.description: This beautifully updated colonial is nestled in a highly desirable neighborhood and location close to parks, dining, highway access, and the array of opportunities surrounding Portage Lakes.  4 Bedrooms upstairs including an Owner's Suite plus an optional 5th bedroom w/closet in the Finished Basement that also features a recreation room and full bathroom. From light fixtures to blinds, the home boasts countless improvements.  A first-floor office with French Doors and the spacious dining room greet you at the front door.  Luxury vinyl tile throughout the first floor.  The eat-in-kitchen is highlighted by an island, granite countertops, pantry, and included stainless steel appliances. Conveniently located mudroom and first floor laundry between the kitchen and garage.  Furnace & A/C replaced in 2020.  Relax on the deck that overlooks a full wrought iron fenced-in backyard. Schedule a private showing today!
